let me testify *

07:00.588 --> 07:03.891
* All these doors that open,
I prefer them to suicide *

07:03.924 --> 07:05.559
* It's a celebration,
come and join the conversation *

07:05.593 --> 07:08.796
* Yeah, you know the reputation,
so, baby *

07:08.829 --> 07:10.998
* Don't ever play yourself

07:11.031 --> 07:14.167
* I, I, I put it on the line

07:14.201 --> 07:16.937
* Every dollar,
every dime, why not *

07:16.970 --> 07:20.140
* I, I, I made it
through the fire... *

07:20.173 --> 07:23.443
-Yo, hold up, hold up, hold up.
-* Came out on the other s...

07:23.477 --> 07:25.813
-I'm still not feeling it, man.
-Wait, wait, wait, wait.

07:25.846 --> 07:27.481
What aren't you feeling,
Carlito?

07:27.515 --> 07:29.149
How you got these two pulling
anchor on this joint.

07:29.182 --> 07:30.818
My songs are blowing up
on SoundCloud right now.

07:30.851 --> 07:32.152
It is what it is, bro.

07:32.185 --> 07:33.487
(scoffs)

07:33.521 --> 07:35.523
Why am I even doing
this stupid showcase?

07:35.556 --> 07:37.357
My talent speaks for itself.

07:37.390 --> 07:38.859
And we're paying for this,
anyways, right?

07:38.892 --> 07:41.428
Wait, hold on, hold on, hold on.
Is that true?

07:41.461 --> 07:42.763
We're paying for this
out of our pocket?

07:42.796 --> 07:44.131
Yo, read your damn contract.

07:44.164 --> 07:46.466
It's under what's called
"an advance."

07:46.500 --> 07:50.437
Aah! I don't believe this
nonsense I'm hearing right now!

07:50.470 --> 07:52.940
Y'all are like
the Misfit Toys up in here.

07:52.973 --> 07:54.808
We won you in the poker game.

07:54.842 --> 07:57.945
And we rescued
old Fred Sanford and Son

07:57.978 --> 08:00.013
right here
from the damn junkyard!

08:00.047 --> 08:02.049
LUCIOUS: Uh, baby, baby, look.
Look, y'all.

08:02.082 --> 08:03.383
Why don't we all
take five minutes

08:03.416 --> 08:05.218
and get on the same page,
all right?

08:05.252 --> 08:06.286
Oh, no, we ain't going nowhere.

08:06.319 --> 08:07.855
Ain't nobody going nowhere!

08:07.888 --> 08:10.824
And, yes, this would be
considered an advance.

08:10.858 --> 08:12.159
But me and Lucious are paying

08:12.192 --> 08:13.794
for this out of our pockets,
okay?

08:13.827 --> 08:15.395
What you need
to be concerned with

08:15.428 --> 08:18.398
is making this song
and the showcase hot!

08:18.431 --> 08:20.834
Then you'll get
your little stacks, okay?

08:20.868 --> 08:25.372
And you best believe I'm taking
my cut, 'cause I did this.

08:25.405 --> 08:28.208
-Yeah, thanks.
-Are we clear?!

08:28.241 --> 08:30.410
Get your ass back on that mic
and sing, come on.

08:30.443 --> 08:32.179
Now-now we good, now?

08:32.212 --> 08:33.814
Yeah, we good.

08:33.847 --> 08:35.315
Okay, big daddy,
take it from the top!

08:35.348 --> 08:37.350
COOKIE: And leave them damn egos
outside.

08:37.384 --> 08:39.352
We don't have room
for them in here, okay?

08:39.386 --> 08:41.188
DEVON: Look, man,
let's-let's just do this.

08:41.221 --> 08:43.090
-Let's just get this over with.
-COOKIE: Yeah.

08:43.123 --> 08:46.326
One, two.
One, two, three.

08:46.359 --> 08:49.229
* Ooh, ooh, ooh, ooh-ooh-ooh,
ooh-ooh-ooh *

08:49.262 --> 08:52.199
* Stop it, no, you can't
