08:59.206 --> 09:01.008
* All this time I thought
falling was breaking... *

09:01.041 --> 09:02.743
Where are we with the venue,
Thirsty?

09:02.776 --> 09:04.778
Oh, it's Gucci, baby. The owner
got a little side-piece,

09:04.812 --> 09:08.181
didn't want wifey to know,
so I got it on cost. (laughs)

09:08.215 --> 09:09.783
My man.

09:09.817 --> 09:12.352
Excuse me.
Miss Williams is here.

09:12.385 --> 09:14.855
Oh, Lord. Becky, what?

09:14.888 --> 09:17.024
Kingsley done sent you
on a spy mission, huh? 007?

09:17.057 --> 09:19.226
-(chuckling)
-No.

09:19.259 --> 09:21.061
Um, no one knows about this yet,

09:21.094 --> 09:22.963
and I didn't want you
to be blindsided,

09:22.996 --> 09:25.132
but Kingsley is vaulting
your entire catalog.

09:25.165 --> 09:28.368
-He's what?
-What does that mean?
-(Cookie sighs)

09:28.401 --> 09:30.437
Um, every single Lucious Lyon
song ever written

09:30.470 --> 09:32.740
and recorded is now on lockdown.

09:32.773 --> 09:35.709
That's gonna slow your residuals
down to a trickle, Pop.

09:35.743 --> 09:37.210
(sighs) Yeah, I'm sorry.
I would've called,

09:37.244 --> 09:39.412
but you blocked me,
so, I'm gonna go.

09:39.446 --> 09:41.281
Thanks, Becky.
Appreciate it.

09:41.314 --> 09:43.617
-Mm-hmm.
-Just blew in
with the bad news, huh?

09:43.651 --> 09:45.118
Those residuals

09:45.152 --> 09:47.054
was the only thing
holding everything together.

09:47.087 --> 09:49.156
I know. I-I know.

09:49.189 --> 09:51.124
That's his ass.

09:51.158 --> 09:52.826
-No, Lucious.
-No, that's his ass!

09:52.860 --> 09:55.128
-Hey, hey.
-Lucious, listen.

09:55.162 --> 09:58.932
Kingsley knows that LFM is about
to do something major,

09:58.966 --> 10:01.134
so he's trying
to throw you off your game.

10:01.168 --> 10:03.036
Don't let him do it.

10:07.941 --> 10:10.410
Hakeem.

10:10.443 --> 10:13.747
Hakeem, I know
you hear me talking to you.

10:13.781 --> 10:16.149
This beef with Blake
is getting out of control.

10:16.183 --> 10:18.652
Babe, you've seen me end it
on Instagram already.

10:18.686 --> 10:21.755
I'm getting death threats,
and that's bad enough.

10:21.789 --> 10:24.124
But today, they k...

10:24.157 --> 10:27.995
They're threatening the kids,
and that's off-limits.

10:28.028 --> 10:30.097
Blake fans are crazy.

10:30.130 --> 10:33.767
Ain't nobody gonna touch you or
the kids, I guarantee you that.

10:33.801 --> 10:35.803
Just talk to Blake.

10:35.836 --> 10:37.671
Please.

10:37.705 --> 10:39.139
I'm scared for the kids.

10:40.674 --> 10:42.309
Okay.

10:42.342 --> 10:44.644
Clean this place up.
It's a damn mess.

10:48.982 --> 10:52.019
Grandma, look. It's Daddy
and Tata singing on TV.

10:52.052 --> 10:54.121
Okay, let me see, baby.

10:54.154 --> 10:55.823
Let me see.

10:59.259 --> 11:01.729
Ooh, it sure is.
Look at that.

11:01.762 --> 11:04.297
-I'm so proud of...
-Ms. Cookie, you have a guest.

11:04.331 --> 11:06.800
Uh, you know what, sweetheart?

11:06.834 --> 11:08.802
Why don't you go

11:08.836 --> 11:11.071
